{
  "texts": [
    "Random Forest addresses some of these limitations by handling larger datasets effectively and providing good accuracy through the aggregation of multiple decision trees (Biswas and Samanta 2021; Kopp et al. 2020).",
    "It also offers insights into feature importance, aiding in identifying critical factors influencing anomalies.",
    "Nevertheless, the computational expense and complexity of interpretation can hinder its application in real-time scenarios.",
    "On the other hand, deep learning techniques like CNNs and LSTMs, have revolutionized anomaly detection.",
    "They can effectively learn and recognize complex data patterns (Khalaf et al. 2019)."
  ]
}